# output/ and postprocessing/output/ are untracked entirely (not just their *.nc contents) since on the
# HPC both are symlinks to scratch space -- git refuses to operate on tracked paths behind a symlinked
# directory ("beyond a symbolic link" fatal errors on stash/checkout/etc). A fresh checkout needs these
# created manually: `mkdir output postprocessing/output` for local dev, or the scratch symlink dance
# documented in conversation history for the HPC.
/output/
/postprocessing/output/
